M|Vers|**Al|** `getItem()` and `setItem()` throw in incognito/private browsing (Safari, Firefox), when quota exceeded, or when disabled.
M|Vers|**Be|** sc evolution via versioning, reduced storage size, prevents storing tk/PII/internal flags.